I need my napkin.

16:00.120 --> 16:01.883
Huh?

16:01.890 --> 16:04.256
Under your drink,
that's my napkin.

16:04.260 --> 16:06.558
Oh, yeah, sure.

16:06.560 --> 16:08.448
God, don't tear it.

16:08.460 --> 16:10.496
Sorry.

16:10.500 --> 16:11.967
[sighs]

16:13.900 --> 16:15.299
What's wrong?

16:15.300 --> 16:17.131
You just melted a really
important phone number.

16:17.140 --> 16:18.767
That's what's wrong.

16:18.770 --> 16:20.306
You and your sweaty glass.

16:22.010 --> 16:24.979
Yeah. It's okay.

16:24.980 --> 16:26.607
See, the ink ran,
but you can see

16:26.610 --> 16:28.339
where the pen pressed
into the napkin.

16:28.350 --> 16:30.238
See? There.

16:31.690 --> 16:33.442
- Thank you.
- Mm.

16:33.460 --> 16:35.758
Sorry about my sweaty glass.

16:35.760 --> 16:37.853
It's okay.

16:37.860 --> 16:40.078
So what do they charge you
for office space around here?

16:40.100 --> 16:42.352
I'm a really good tipper.

16:42.360 --> 16:45.056
Long day at the office?
Can I get you something to eat?

16:46.770 --> 16:48.590
Suppose I'm meeting someone?

16:48.600 --> 16:50.158
You're not.

16:50.170 --> 16:51.592
How do you know that?

16:51.610 --> 16:53.464
Well, you ordered
a second drink.

16:53.480 --> 16:54.708
If you were meeting someone

16:54.710 --> 16:55.870
you would've nursed
your first drink.

16:57.510 --> 17:00.001
