20:19.210 --> 20:21.701
Not all the time.
Just lately.

20:21.720 --> 20:23.347
Since you've been
spending time in Rosewood.

20:23.350 --> 20:26.012
Yeah, well, it can have
that effect on you.

20:26.020 --> 20:27.681
Then why do you keep
going back there?

20:30.790 --> 20:34.920
- Do you know what I wanna do?
- What do you wanna do?

20:34.930 --> 20:38.422
Do you remember that bar
off Columbus where we first met?

20:38.430 --> 20:41.092
Yes, I do.

20:41.100 --> 20:44.297
Well, I wanna go back there

20:44.310 --> 20:47.199
and buy you a drink.

20:47.210 --> 20:49.201
And I wanna go back there
and flirt with you

20:49.210 --> 20:52.441
and start all over again.

20:52.450 --> 20:54.941
Is that something
that might interest you?

20:54.950 --> 20:58.477
I'm waving wi-uh-uh-uh-wild

21:01.820 --> 21:04.709
Elliott's not gonna help us.
