21:04.730 --> 21:07.619
Okay, something does not include
making a deal with the devil.

21:07.630 --> 21:09.791
Besides, you heard him,
Mary cannot get in there

21:09.800 --> 21:11.222
anymore than we can.

21:11.230 --> 21:12.561
Okay, but what if
we did it together?

21:12.570 --> 21:14.219
If we used Mary Drake
to get us in.

