No, Emily, it's not happening.

21:16.100 --> 21:18.591
Hey, look, I'm not saying
that we let her in the club.

21:18.610 --> 21:20.737
I'm not even saying
that we should trust her.

21:20.740 --> 21:22.731
But we need a way to Ali
and right now

21:22.740 --> 21:25.607
Mary Drake is the closest thing
to a key that we've got.

21:25.610 --> 21:27.168
We don't know anything
about her.

21:27.180 --> 21:29.978
You know more about her
than anybody else.

21:29.980 --> 21:32.119
You were in there, Spencer.

21:32.120 --> 21:35.487
In Radley, before the designer
cocktails and the valet parking.

21:35.490 --> 21:37.981
You were locked in there.

21:37.990 --> 21:39.321
You know how that feels.

21:39.330 --> 21:41.059
And you know what
that can do to a person.

21:45.530 --> 21:47.589
Rollins talked to Jason?

21:47.600 --> 21:48.919
That's what he said.

21:48.940 --> 21:50.191
According to Toby,
that's something

21:50.200 --> 21:51.997
that nobody else
has managed to do.

21:52.010 --> 21:53.762
Are the police looking
for Jason?

21:53.780 --> 21:56.499
Toby is. He needs someone
to confirm Mary Drake's story.

21:57.610 --> 21:59.771
Confirmation
other than her face?

21:59.780 --> 22:02.248
People don't seem to remember
Ali's mother having a sister.

22:04.220 --> 22:05.812
When do you meet with Liam?

22:05.820 --> 22:07.617
Uh, 4 o'clock.

22:08.690 --> 22:10.885
Can we make this work with him?

22:10.890 --> 22:13.358
Of course, we can
make it work. I think.

22:13.360 --> 22:15.954
At least long enough
to finish the book.

22:15.960 --> 22:17.791
I was in_ such a rush
to get It over with

22:17.800 --> 22:19.324
that I broke up with him
before he told me

22:19.330 --> 22:20.820
that he was back on the book.

22:20.840 --> 22:23.035
I really complicated
the situation.

22:25.370 --> 22:28.009
All due respect,
things have been complicated

22:28.010 --> 22:29.637
for quite some time.

22:29.640 --> 22:32.347
This book means as much
to Liam as it does to us

22:32.350 --> 22:33.647
and that's why
he wants to work on it.

22:33.650 --> 22:35.140
Yeah, it might mean
as much to him

22:35.150 --> 22:37.710
but it does not mean
the same things.

22:40.820 --> 22:43.709
I promise I will make this work.

22:49.600 --> 22:52.626
