Emily, no!‘

37:33.910 --> 37:36.105
No!

37:36.120 --> 37:37.439
No!

37:40.290 --> 37:41.712
What happened to her?

37:41.720 --> 37:43.984
She wasn't like that
when she came here.

37:43.990 --> 37:47.153
Miss Drake,
I'd like a word with you.

37:51.770 --> 37:53.397
No one's to come in.

38:01.580 --> 38:03.400
You're not supposed
to be here.

38:03.410 --> 38:05.298
I've been calling you
for two days.

38:11.350 --> 38:13.580
[indistinct talking]

38:14.990 --> 38:17.515
Your being here
is not part of the plan.

38:17.520 --> 38:19.659
