38:28.870 --> 38:31.930
Listen to me.

38:31.940 --> 38:33.339
Don't.

38:37.310 --> 38:39.175
- Hello.
- Hey.

38:41.820 --> 38:44.539
- Dad's private stock.
- Mm-hmm.

38:44.550 --> 38:45.949
